8. Open the `Views\Manage\EnableAuthenticator.cshtml` file and replace the following line

```
<div id="qrCodeData" data-url="@Html.Raw(Model.AuthenticatorUri)"></div>
```

with

```
<div id="qrCodeData" data-url="@Model.AuthenticatorUri"></div>
```

remove the call to `Html.Raw()`.

9. Recompile your application and test you can generate 2fa recovery codes correctly, then redeploy your application.

